{"tid":23464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［圖］已消失的九龍聖山","createTime":"2016-12-05T02:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T14:30:12.000Z","uid":21225,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6799e4dc68b4334d5e10a79649993af791ae1f8c","tid":23464,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"宋王臺原本 是九龍城淺灘南岸的一座天然山丘，高度為海拔35米，又稱「聖山」。九龍城在宋代為朝廷的鹽場，後世相傳宋王臺是宋帝的石殿遺跡，晚清期間山頂的巨石被刻 上「宋王臺」三字，開埠初年在口耳相傳下，一班西方漢學家與華人學者、紳商和街坊吹捧為宋代古跡。<br />\n<br />\n19世紀末期，有人在宋王臺聖山採石作建築材料，對古蹟造成威脅。香港立法局華人議員何啟支持九龍城居民發起的保存宋王臺運動，1898年8月15日在立法局提出動議，要求政府立法保存宋王臺古蹟。1899年，立法局通過《保存宋王臺條例》，禁止在宋王臺聖山採石。在20世紀初期，政府接受中國商人的捐款，環山築成石基，建成一個花園。這塊巨岩下面平滑，一半枕在山頂生成的大石上；其餘一半空虛，祇由一顆小石卵支撐。<br />\n<br />\n在香港日治時期，啟德機場需要被擴建成兩條交叉跑道。在1943年1月9日，由日本的宇津木法師領導祭祀，然後經多次爆破，炸毀了整塊巨岩，連帶在宋王臺後方的名勝珓杯石亦一併炸毀。工程尚未完工，日本已宣佈投降，香港重光。<br />\n<br />\n聖山位置大約位於啟德機場客運大樓一帶，「宋王臺」石碑後來被遷移到距離約300呎的現址放置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Wf13om.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Wf13om.jpg&h=938b7b8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyMuB24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyMuB24.jpg&h=90af8908&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/05/105240_7a86bad0792dce7015cda760719bd776.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F05%2F105240_7a86bad0792dce7015cda760719bd776.jpg&h=ce6c6fe8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32t73o3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32t73o3.jpg&h=c86d4a17&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79d4y3N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79d4y3N.jpg&h=89595018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/05/105254_8c5c35e1ad5de4a6e2921cfadac3d6ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F05%2F105254_8c5c35e1ad5de4a6e2921cfadac3d6ec.jpg&h=d9e9d352&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Q92OJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Q92OJM.jpg&h=bda5a9ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31e04ac7e06720e6d7a8d05e4422a29ab30994fd","tid":23464,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"昔日的聖山，位於今日宋皇台道和譚公道、北帝街東北面一帶。東面臨海，其餘三面都是稻田和池塘，人跡罕至。每逢登山日，一眾文人雅士先行聚集於陳步墀的別業「暢龢室」。據陳步墀解釋，暢龢二字出自《蘭亭集序》 : 「&hellip;&hellip;是日也，天朗氣清，蕙風和暢&hellip;&hellip;」另外，「和」與「龢」同義 （「暢龢室」大約位於九龍寨城南面，即今日太子道一帶）從「暢龢室」南行不遠就看到一個指示牌，寫著「宋行宮故址」。指示遊人到達聖山的路徑。再穿過一條小橋，下有河流，前行不遠，就到達聖山入口的石牌坊。上面橫着一個石匾，刻有「宋臺舊址」四個字。兩邊鎸有石聯，乃出自明末遺民陳獨漉的詩句 :「一聲望帝啼荒殿，百戰山河見落暉。」"},{"pid":"8206e1d7b3d6edc9b859f4545f9e0a17164dc52b","tid":23464,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f971a65988f0a2b44d69c395bb3f2a3d4d2d828","tid":23464,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imrE9Y1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FimrE9Y1.jpg&h=52f4d96b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家宋王臺公園好無霸氣好唔顯眼咁<br />\n但以前真係有種威嚴感覺係度"},{"pid":"e569021f38b07f17657270cecebe787b24e7f4c7","tid":23464,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e9c999829ad6fb4c70712a1b0f28c581ca9b29","tid":23464,"uid":8174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T07:46:52.000Z","msg":"巴打出親都高質post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2289d16c6fa046afcf6edfbca17982348a34d66","tid":23464,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打出親都高質post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係想喚起大家對香港史嘅關注姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7398ef62b8564cc6e6c6695c80940f3495db11d","tid":23464,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ca017b8c73236c2f377060eb7fd0dfe868b295","tid":23464,"uid":17224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337f47ab0609be8ccbb171ebf9e21ac608fef66a","tid":23464,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拜見宋帝<br />\n<br />\n其實仲可以引伸到去本土宗教度<br />\n九龍城 大澳 東涌都有侯王廟<br />\n而侯王就係跟隨宋帝護駕嘅將軍楊亮節<br />\n當時佢就係死係香港一帶<br />\n所以世界上好似啲五間侯王廟 一間深圳一間廣州三間香港<br />\n<br />\n而九龍城侯王廟同聖山位置 再加埋之前沙中線發現到嘅古蹟 應該係互有關聯"},{"pid":"7b89ff2c07412136674b1db4bffb9a8d25481665","tid":23464,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T00:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98edb7ebf2e1a1351be4bf9a776b7f0f80f18e9","tid":23464,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:17:05.000Z","msg":"好中意睇呢d香港歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ccb5b26dd1b6a3555bbfe99262311060b3628a","tid":23464,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6593f41d6f385038220e85d57ae3efaa72752836","tid":23464,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:38:02.000Z","msg":"巴打下次講下維多利亞城界碑<br />\n<br />\n第7塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3b1926b0404cf088b25d0de01264be15fc37fa","tid":23464,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打下次講下維多利亞城界碑<br />\n<br />\n第7塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbbda0043f0042246215292d3b6f8cd89b93c68b","tid":23464,"uid":13614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係要講多d香港史呀"},{"pid":"42a0cb50bb4b338a2f8497b408bafdf3d693f979","tid":23464,"uid":58409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打 想聽下街名由來"}]}